 Apocalypse and Guiledart landed at the Sulaco.
Neptune had intercepted the comm and headed towards
the sulaco and had motioned the new girl to follow. He
landed a few seconds after Apocalypse. "He came back
sooner then expected." said guiledart. Apocalypse
smiled. "Yes now I can have some real fun." He walked
into the Sulaco looked around and saw a lot of old
faces. He was surprised by cerberus. "I see hes back.
What about Dachande?" Guiledart and Neptune kept quiet
as the usualy did. Guiledart walked over to the
counter. He dusted of the pads. "Our signal jammers
are still here. That could be usefull later."
